#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As of &productnamereg; 12 SP1, you can run multiple Apache instances on the "
"same server. This has several advantages over running multiple virtual hosts "
"(see <xref linkend=\"sec.apache2.configuration.manually.vhost\"/>):"
